Switzerland-Italy Tax Talks Reach Difficulties, Le Matin Says

-- B y   T h o m a s   M u l i e r
-- 
2011-07-17T09:49:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/switzerland-italy-tax-talks-reach-difficulties-le-matin-says.html
Switzerland ’s talks over income
taxes on Italians working in Switzerland have reached
difficulties,  Le Matin  said, citing Roland Meier, spokesman for
Switzerland’s finance ministry.  The Swiss canton of Ticino froze half of 57 million francs
($70 million) from 2010 that it normally transfers to  Italy ,
worsening the dispute, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
